full_text: I'm throwing in with Keith. I got $12 and some change, a Bic and some pocket lint. https://t.co/O0eQj9rAe2

If growing up in Cleveland wasn't enough, many of the players would stop in at DiBela's pizza on Larchmere after the games. I attended school near there and spent a lot of time at DiBellas when there wasn't anything else to do. Great times when Cavs would show up. https://t.co/VDRUCpqieK
